Hey @jakub_zaniewski89 Hi @meetsingh1427

How are you? :slightly_smiling_face:

So I'm going to try and help you with your career planning and Emma should have given you a brief bit of background on me already.

Feel free to introduce yourself, say a little bit about what you would like to get out of the mentorship and continue chatting within this channel. :wave:

Perhaps we could start with what it is you study at school and what subjects you like to spend your time on? Do you have any other ideas of what jobs you might like to try in the future?

I've done LOADS of jobs so can certainly give you some insights
PS: You can message me any time you like by the way. Anytime a question comes to mind or you want to have a chat! I will try to reply as soon as I can :slightly_smiling_face:
